  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResolvingHint

    public class DomResolveConverter<T extends DomElement>
extends ResolvingConverter<T>
    Converter which resolves DomElements by name in a defined scope. The scope is taken from corresponding DomFileDescription.getResolveScope(GenericDomValue).
